{
  "stem": "6924.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But during sitting in that hole there, in the village, where we were hidden, I always had in my mind that if we'll survive, I am not gonna stay in that land, Poland, where so much Jewish blood was spilled.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And thinking about a family, the only thought was how to get out of that Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That always was on my mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once we got married, I had to start working there for the Russians there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I [? needed ?] something to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Got to make a living.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But my mind was set up to get out of Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And next year, my daughter was born.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And people are starting to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Jews started to leave already Poland for Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The place, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Belsen ?] camps.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "From there, we heard you can go to United States, to Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we started out, also, after my daughter was-- there was-- my daughter was born in '44.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in '45-- in '40-- '45, my daughter was born in '45.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We married in '44.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And after-- in '45-- and-- in '46, we got finally, decided we should go-- no, the same year, yet, in '45, we decided to leave Poland and go to Germany, to [?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Czechoslovakia. ?] It wasn't an easy ride, with plenty problems.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But finally, we made it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We came to Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The problems was-- was with a baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we left Poland, she was a few-- a few months old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And wasn't-- we had to go by train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- then was problems.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to cross a border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we made it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in Germany, we stayed in Deggendorf and DP, Deggendorf, for one year, until we got the affidavit visa to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just want to tell you that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
